Subject: [PATCH 2/3] dt-bindings: sound: tas57xx: add ti,tas5713 compatible

Add the TAS5713 25W stereo Class-D amplifier to the list of supported
compatible strings in the tas57xx device tree binding.

Signed-off-by: Petr Parkan Janda <petronijus@bastla.com>
